introduction:
Week 5 and it’s now anybody’s league. We’re into the thicc of things now. Fantasy Football is lost during the draft, but won on the waiver wire. Will big pickups like Damien Williams catapult teams into playoff contention while other teams sit holding their dicks in their hands get left behind? 
 
Thanks for the 9 votes we received this week, repeat non-voters will see their rankings drop if I have anything to say about it. 

Week 5, lubed up and ready to go.
